Package: vivoFlux
Title: Calculate and visualize in vivo metabolic fluxes based on 13-carbon tracing 
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Bo",
           family = "Yuan",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "bo_yuan@hsph.harvard.edu",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-0222-8095"))
Description: This package performs natural abundance correction, visualize the 13-carbon labeling enrichment, and calculates absolute fluxes of circulating metabolites interconverting between each other, and the direct fluxes into TCA cycle.  
